OL,3,CFather handed hospital order after
OL,4,Ckilling his newborn son
OL,6,FA father who broke every bone in his
OL,7,Fnewborn son's skull when he smashed
OL,8,Fhim up against a wall has been handed
OL,9,Fa hospital order.
OL,11,FKadees Mohammed, 31, woke up in the
OL,12,Fmiddle of the night and killed his
OL,13,Fthree-week-old son Ibrahim and
OL,14,Fattacked his wife and mother with an
OL,15,Firon when they tried desperately to
OL,16,Fstop him at the family home in Dovey
OL,17,FRoad, Birmingham, on October 18 2022.
