OL,3,CFather handed hospital order after
OL,4,Ckilling his newborn son
OL,6,FThe court heard he had suffered from
OL,7,Fundiagnosed schizophrenia and was
OL,8,Fordered to be detained at a secure
OL,9,Fmental health facility on Monday.
OL,11,FBirmingham Crown Court heard that in
OL,12,Fthe weeks before the attack his work
OL,13,Fcolleagues believed that he may have
OL,14,FADHD and may have been struggling with
OL,15,Fhis sexuality.
