OL,3,CFather handed hospital order after
OL,4,Ckilling his newborn son
OL,6,FMr Justice Choudhury said the incident
OL,7,Fwas the "prodrome to severe psychotic
OL,8,Fmental illness", before adding: "The
OL,9,Ftragedy is that your condition was
OL,10,Fundiagnosed until it was too late."
OL,12,FMohammed was convicted of manslaughter
OL,13,Fon the basis of diminished
OL,14,Fresponsibility and two counts of
OL,15,Fwounding on 7 November.
OL,17,FThe court was told he had been a
OL,18,F"model patient" at the secure facility
OL,19,Fhe has been detained in in the West
OL,20,FMidlands.
