OL,6,FThe defendant, who appeared at his
OL,7,Fsentencing hearing via video-link,
OL,8,Fappeared to listen intently to
OL,9,Fproceedings.
OL,11,FIn a tribute to her baby released
OL,12,Fthrough West Midlands Police,
OL,13,FIbrahim's mother said: "My love for
OL,14,Fyou is eternal.
OL,16,F"I know that you are no longer with me
OL,17,Fbut your precious belongings are so
OL,18,Fdear to me."
