OL,6,F"I imagine how life would have been
OL,7,Fwith you by my side. I would have
OL,8,Fwatched you grow, laughed with you and
OL,9,Fwiped your tears."
OL,11,F"You will remain in my memories for
OL,12,Fthe rest of my life like a beautiful
OL,13,Fflower. Love from your mum."
